==========================================================================

    OpenTTD requires the original Windows version of "Transport Tycoon
    Deluxe" data files in order to function.  Copy the following files
    to ${DATADIR}/data/ directory:

	sample.cat
	trg1r.grf
	trgcr.grf
	trghr.grf
	trgir.grf
	trgtr.grf

    Enjoy!!

==========================================================================
